4. **Condition representation / AND implementation**\
- `WhereClause` holds one `ConditionList` ([WhereClause.java](/Users/megha_shah/Documents/Ren_Proj/DBMS/SEMANTIC/AST_NODES/WhereClause.java))\
- `ConditionList` holds `List<UnaryCondition>` ([ConditionList.java](/Users/megha_shah/Documents/Ren_Proj/DBMS/SEMANTIC/AST_NODES/ConditionList.java))\
- `UnaryCondition` = `Identifier columnName + Operator operator + Literal value` ([UnaryCondition.java](/Users/megha_shah/Documents/Ren_Proj/DBMS/SEMANTIC/AST_NODES/UnaryCondition.java))\
- `AND` is implemented by looping all unary conditions and short-circuiting on first false (`for ... if !evaluate => false`).\
